{"tid":2319751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅冠聰撚到港共好嬲好嬲","createTime":"2020-12-10T09:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T15:57:54.000Z","uid":277640,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"48d238e8d43efd0273f0a38771e7551a60cc69d3","tid":2319751,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"牙聰同李宇軒的妹妹 見主導BNO計劃嘅英國內政大臣彭黛玲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會面合照以英國國旗和特區區旗作背景　<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">特區政府：強烈不滿及反感</span></span> (港共真係好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，這明顯是英國政府近日繼發表惡意中傷特區的「香港半年報告」後另一次<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">挑釁</span></strong></span>行為，並指英方對《中英聯合聲明》和持BNO護照港人的言論，更是有違國際義務。 <br />\n<br />\n發言人指。。。。英國政府若刻意違背承諾，不顧中央人民政府的堅決反對和一再交涉，執意利用部分港人仍持有BNO護照或有關身分進行政治炒作，以人權和自由為幌子<span class=\"red\">(乜撚嘢幌子，係要用啲支那term)</span>，向有關人士提供在英居留和入籍路徑，是罔顧歷史事實，有違其國際義務。 <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">究竟邊個毁約在先，真係面皮幾尺厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講得出就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2370021/彭黛玲羅冠聰在英國旗和特區旗前合照-港府強烈不滿及反感\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2370021%2F%E5%BD%AD%E9%BB%9B%E7%8E%B2%E7%BE%85%E5%86%A0%E8%81%B0%E5%9C%A8%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E5%92%8C%E7%89%B9%E5%8D%80%E6%97%97%E5%89%8D%E5%90%88%E7%85%A7-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E5%BC%B7%E7%83%88%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E5%8F%8A%E5%8F%8D%E6%84%9F&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYprc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=6488b8e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2370021/彭黛玲羅冠聰在英國旗和特區旗前合照-港府強烈不滿及反感</